OL,3,CMan charged with murder following baby
OL,4,Cdeath
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murder following the death of a
OL,8,Fbaby in Salisbury.
OL,10,FJamie Fulford, 26, of Tournament Road,
OL,11,Fappeared at Salisbury Magistrates
OL,12,FCourt on Friday 8th May, charged with
OL,13,Fmurder and causing or allowing harm/
OL,14,Fdeath of a child.
OL,16,FIt follows the death of a baby boy in
OL,17,F2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
