OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778263866
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following baby
OL,4,Cdeath
OL,6,FThe four week old boy was admitted to
OL,7,FSalisbury District Hospital On
OL,8,FSeptember 1st 2022, with serious
OL,9,Finjuries. He died just over a week
OL,10,Flater, on September 9th.
OL,12,FFulford has been remanded in custody
OL,13,Funtil May 12th when he will next
OL,14,Fappear at Winchester Crown Court.
OL,16,FThe baby's mother, Sophie Egerton, 22,
OL,17,Fof Tournament Road, is charged with
OL,18,Fcausing or allowing harm/death of a
OL,19,Fchild.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
